/***************
    Package.json
****************/
=> First File of the application
Go to folder with cmd/terminal
Step1
    => npm init
Step2
    => Answer questions
    {
        "name": "learnpackage",
        "version": "1.0.0",
        "description": "this is about packages",
        "main": "index.js",
        "scripts": {
            "test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\" && exit 1"
        },
        "keywords": [
            "react",
            "redux"
        ],
        "author": "nareshit",
        "license": "ISC"
    }
Step3
    => Type yes
    => Press enter

/***************
   local
****************/
Local to folder
Step to package
=> npm install <package name> --save
=> npm install zone.js --save
=> By Default Always latest version
=> npm i react@15.0.1
~ install minor updated version(16.8) (16.9)
^ install major version(16.8)(17.0)
=> they are directly connected with application

/***************
    Global
****************/
Global to the system
=> To generate
=> development
=> run
=> test

Window
=> Run your cmd as admin
    =>npm install -g <package name>
    =>npm install -g @aakashdeveloper/create-node-app

Mac/linux
=> Must use sudo befor command
    => sudo npm install -g <package name>
    => sudo npm install -g @aakashdeveloper/create-node-app

/***************
    Setup react in System
****************/
Step1>
    Window
    => Run your cmd as admin
        =>npm install -g create-react-app

    Mac/linux
    => Must use sudo befor command
        => sudo npm install -g create-react-app

Step2>
    GO inside folder where you want app
    cd Desktop/folder/classes/July_react_evng

Step3>
    create-react-app <appname>
    create-react-app firstapp

Step4>
    cd firstapp

Step5>
    npm start


/*********************************
   Commands in Package.json
**********************************/
Default command => npm start
Other Command => npm run <command>


/*********************************
  Type Of Component
**********************************/
Functional Component        ||       Class Base Component
Light in Weigth                         They are heavy as compare to Functional
Display Component                       Logical Component
cannot handle state                     can handle state

