/*********************************
        State And Props
**********************************/

=> State act like a local variable
=> Props is the helping us to transfer state of
    one componet to another

Component A            Component B
             props
State A -------------------->State B
***************************************
=> In state we can assign the data  
=> In props we can only recive the data
******************************************
=> Data intercation in class component happen
   through state
=> Data interaction in functional component
   happen through props


